name: Jess
Lore: 'Popular musician. Often seen with Bib Fortuna. Captivates those around her. Hoping to join a band and leave Jabba''s palace.',
Text: 'May retrieve 1 Force each time you deploy a musician to same site. During your turn, may use 1 Force to ''charm'' one male alien of ability < 3 present; that male is forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn.',
